snippet.title: Nullstar: Solus | First Look | indie.io
snippet.description:
Wishlist Nullstar: Solus now on Steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3094210/Nullstar_Solus/ 

Be Faster! Fly through a world at its end, take on 80 different levels as a solitary scav drone, and collect the remnants of a fallen city's nullstar. Navigate a megastructure filled with traps and guardians of a past age, the ruins of a civilization where not all is as it might seem.
